title: For Sale:  Small Mostly Complete Interceptor Body Armor
postcontent: Due to some unforeseen financial circumstances I have to try to sell my IBA. This armor is real and was issued to me during OIF6-7. It is legally mine and can be sold because it is a "combat loss". I was hit by a VBIED while wearing this armor and it saved my life. It has some small fragmentation holes peppered throughout the front face but it's not really noticeable and in no way decreases the functionality of the armor. I wore this system for 17 months overseas so there is sweat stains on it, they can be washed out if desired. It comes with the Outer Tactical Vest (OTV),The OTV features a carrier shell, and three main ballistic panel inserts (left and right side panels, and a rear back panel), which are made with a finely woven kevlar  KM2 fiber. It also comes with Enhanced Side Ballistic Inserts (ESBIs). It also includes the Throat yoke and groin protector that both have kevlar inserts in them. I don't have the Front SAPI or back SAPI plates due the explosion but I can vouch this armor system will do what it was designed to do with minimal trauma. I don't what this exactly goes for but if interested send me a message with an offer and we'll take it from there. God bless and I hope you never find yourself in a situation where you would need this system but if you do, it will work.
